These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-8-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, december, march, june
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, argentine, indian, thai
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, musical, fantasy, family
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, cycling, parkour, water-polo
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bus, skateboard, subway
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the thai##5
 3. the argentine is on the far left##1
 4. the mexican is the person who's sport is cycling##1
 5. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the mexican##1
 6. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8
 7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 8. the person who's sport is parkour is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8
 9. the person driving the subway is the person who's birthday is in july##1
10. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##5
11. the person who's birthday is in december is in an even position##4
12. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
13. the person watching family movies is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##8
14. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
15. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##5
16. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
| Birthday    | june | december     | march     | july |
| Nationality        | argentine  | mexican | indian      | thai      |
| Movie-Genre         | family  | musical    | fantasy | western       |
| Sport       | baseball | cycling   | parkour      | water-polo  |
| Transport   | bus      | airplane  | skateboard   | subway      |

