.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-8-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, gospel, indie, disco
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, baseball, swimming, weightlifting
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, firefighter, manager, police-officer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, epic, horror, romance
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, yellow, light-blue, emerald
 1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 2. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
 3. the police-officer is not to the left of the person watching epic movies##8
 4. the designer is between the firefighter and the manager##2
 5. the designer is not the person who likes light-blue##6
 6. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the left of the police-officer##5
 7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the person who likes azure##8
 8. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the left of the police-officer##5
 9. the designer is somewhere to the right of the person watching adventure movies##5
10. the person who's sport is baseball is in an odd position##4
11. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
12. the person who likes light-blue is not to the right of the person who likes azure##8
13. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5
14. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the fan of disco##1
15. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the left of the person watching romance movies##8
16. the person who likes azure is not to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##8
17. the person who's sport is baseball is the fan of gospel##1
18. the fan of gospel is not the firefighter##6
19. the fan of reggae is not the person who's sport is swimming##6
20. the fan of disco is somewhere to the right of the designer##5
21. the firefighter is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5

.:: Answer ::.
