 9. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the right of the fan of r&b##8
10. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
11. the person driving the bike is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
12. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
13. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##8
14. the person who's sport is handball is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##8
15. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
